@startuml
title ASR Cloud.ru Whisper MVP Flow

actor Client
participant "AI Platform\n/v1/asr/transcribe" as API
participant "ASR Service" as ASR
participant "Cloud.ru Foundation Models\nWhisper" as Cloud
database "Safe ASR JSONL log" as Log
participant "RouterV2 / /v1/decide" as Router

Client -> API: multipart/form-data\nfile=<audio>
API -> API: validate one file,\nmedia type, max size
API -> ASR: transcribe(audio bytes,\nmetadata only)
ASR -> Cloud: POST configurable path\nBearer API key, model, file
Cloud --> ASR: transcript response
ASR --> API: typed transcript result
API -> Log: safe metadata only\n(no audio, no transcript)
API --> Client: transcript JSON

note over API, Router
ASR endpoint does not call RouterV2 or /v1/decide.
Client may submit transcript to /v1/decide explicitly in a separate request.
end note

@enduml
